==French==
===Transitive verb===
'''faire'''

# to [[do]]
#:''faire la vaisselle'' - to do the washing-up
# to [[make]]
#:''faire une erreur'' - to make a mistake
# to [[make]] (someone do something)
#:''Tu me fais rire.'' - You make me laugh.
# (''temperature, weather; impersonal'')
#: ''Il fait chaud.'' - It's hot.

